		</a>
	</div>
</footer>
<style>
	footer {
		padding: 2em 1em 4em 1em;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0e1b35 0%, #0b1220 100%);
		color: #9fb3d9;
		text-align: center;
	}
	
	.social-links {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 1em;
		margin-top: 1em;
	}
	
	.social-links a {
		text-decoration: none;
		color: #9fb3d9;
		padding: 0.5em;
		border-radius: 6px;
		transition: all 0.2s ease;
	}
	
	.social-links a:hover {
		color: #0ea5e9;
		background-color: rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.1);
	}
</style>
